                        <div id="page-title">
                            Tasteless Recreation of a Pollock
                        </div>
                    

                    

                    



                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<div style="text-align: right;"><div class="page-rate-widget-box"><span class="rate-points">rating:&nbsp;<span class="number prw54353">+17</span></span><span class="rateup btn btn-default"><a title="I like it" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, 1)">+</a></span><span class="ratedown btn btn-default"><a title="I don't like it" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, -1)">&#8211;</a></span><span class="cancel btn btn-default"><a title="Cancel my vote" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.cancelVote(event)">x</a></span></div></div>
<div style="font-weight: bold;">
<p><span style="color: #d62929">So, remind me again, Elliot, why are we here?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">It's good inspiration.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Well, this is the fourth time this week you've walled yourself in here.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">A small price to pay.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">I'm concerned about you.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">There's no reason you should be.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Elliot&#8230;</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Lana, I'm fine.</span></p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">What have you even been doing in here?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Research.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Research?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Mhm.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">How?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Well, come here&#8230; Oh come on, just lay down, I don't bite.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">That's debatable.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Heh&#8230; alright&#8230; what are you doing?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Just watching you.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">I'm not the interesting thing here.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Elliot, we're in an empty room, what else is there?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">The paintings.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">What?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Lookup.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Holy shit&#8230;</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">They're not that impressive.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">They’re amazing.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Eh.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Were these here the entire time?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Yes, you didn't notice?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Well, no, I was too busy making sure you're not doing something stupid.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Mmmm&#8230;</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">&#8230; So remind me again, why can't you do this at home?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">I need a dark place to create an illusion.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Well, I can cover up the studio windows.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Why would you do that?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Well, I want you to be comfy.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">It’s comfy here.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">I have a hard time believing that.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">I dunno, something about this asbestos-filled junk pile really just kicks my mind into gear, ya feel?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Elliot.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Yes?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">You realize that asbestos can harm your lungs right?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">I'm not an idiot Lana&#8230; I just don't care.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">What? Why?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Well, like here let me just show you.</span></p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Elliot.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Yes.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">That's the Mona Lisa.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">It is&#8230; is there something wrong with that?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">What does this have to do with you slowly killing yourself?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">You’ll see.</span></p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Elliot, seriously I'm getting sick of your shit. What do these paintings have to do with you?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Well, they’re all famous. They’re classics. They’ll be remembered for generations to come! They're priceless gems that could never be replaced.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Your life is too.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">&#8230;</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">It is Elliot.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Eh.</span></p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">So why do this anyway? Why stare at these paintings for hours in this scummy old place? You can go to a museum, you could look them up, you coul-</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Sh, sh, sh, I could. I could do all of that, but, I don't know if it would quite match me and my methods.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Oh yes, because getting lung cancer is better than sitting in a museum and taking a photo of a painting.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">It could be.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">What?!</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Well, like, look around you, at all of these paintings and tell me what makes them famous.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Elliot.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">What?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">You're not serious, right?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">About?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Oh my god&#8230; dying doesn't make your work famous.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Arguable.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Elliot! Oh my god, there's tons of living artists all over who are known worldwide.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Yes, but their work isn't priceless. They can always produce another piece, but Rembrandt can't create another portrait.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Elliot&#8230; times have changed.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Really, how would they have changed?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">There's the Internet now.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Lana, look at me. The Internet has a lot of fads, a lot of passing trends and with those trends go us artists.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">You're looking at this backwards.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">I'd say the same to you.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">You won't become famous because of your death.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">My pieces will be priceless though.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">No, they won't.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">They will.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Elliot, seriously, stop.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">&#8230;</span></p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Lana. Have I ever told you about my paintings from New Orleans?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">I didn't even know you've went.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Well, I went years ago, I was a kid with my dad and we had just bought three paintings. One of jazz players, one of the French Quarters, and another of a graveyard. Now we couldn't take these through the airport, so we had to ship them.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Shipping sucks.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Really does, so we got them appraised. The lady kept on telling us about our terrible investments-</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">She sounds shitty.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">-and didn't stop until she reached the jazz players. She stopped and gawked at us before telling us about how this makes up for everything and blah, blah, blah. She went off on a rant about how he was dying and how she doesn't think he'd make it through the hurricane season.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Was she wrong?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">No. I sold the piece for triple it's price.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Elliot&#8230;</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Yes.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">You don't have to be dead to be famous.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">No, but it sure does help.</span></p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Elliot. What is that?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">What?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Those canvases?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Failed attempts at fame.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">What do&#8230; oh my god&#8230; Elliot&#8230;</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">I know, they look like tasteless recreation of a Pollock.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Elliot.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Yes?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">You need help.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">I’m fine.</span></p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Lana, why are you still here?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">I’m concerned about you.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">There’s no reason to be.</span></p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Elliot.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Yes.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">What were you doing in Indiana?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">I was seeing my uncle.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Really?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Yes.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Elliot&#8230;</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Yes?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Seriously, tell me.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">I’m being serious.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Elliot.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">&#8230;</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">&#8230;</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">&#8230; I was buying explosives&#8230; you can get a fourth a stick over there&#8230;</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Oh.</span></p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Lana. Are you mad at me?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">I’m just concerned.</span></p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Lana, are you going to leave?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Not without you.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">&#8230;</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">&#8230;</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">You have to eat soon.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">So do you.</span></p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Lana, what are you doing over there?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Just looking.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Looking for what?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Nothing, I’m just looking.</span></p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Lana.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Yes.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Can you just leave?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">No.</span></p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Lana?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Not leaving.</span></p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Don’t you care about me?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">I’m not leaving you to die.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">You wouldn’t be leaving me.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">I would.</span></p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Lana?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Yes?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Who have you been texting?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">My mother, she’s concerned about me.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Oh.</span></p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">You’re a fucking bitch.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">What?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">You fucking lied!</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">What? Hey! Dude chill!</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">You fucking called me in! Didn’t you?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Elliot chill.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">You fucking called me in!</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Elliot, chill. Deep breaths.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Don’t tell me what to do!</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">Elliot.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Don’t fucking touch me.</span></p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Fuck you.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">You’re being a child.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">I’m not going in.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">You really don’t have a choice.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">I do.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">&#8230; you aren’t.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Watch me&#8230; Get your grubby fucking hands off of me!</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">No!</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Fucking bitch!</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">&#8230;</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Lana?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">&#8230;</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Lana?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #d62929">&#8230;</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #2222b4">Oh fuck&#8230; Lana?</span></p>
</div>

